<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 887/85 of 2 April 1985 amending Regulation (EEC) No 1726/70 as regards the system of supervision of first processing and market preparation of leaf tobacco </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 887/85, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1726/70 seoses lehttubaka esmat&ouml;&ouml;tlemise ja pakendamise j&auml;relevalves&uuml;steemiga 2. aprill 1985 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 727/70 of 21 April 1970 on the common organization of the market in raw tobacco (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1461/82 (2), and in particular the first subparagraph of Article 3 (3) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 21. aprilli 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 727/70 toortubakaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1461/82, (2) eriti selle artikli 3 l&otilde;ike 3 esimest l&otilde;iku, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1726/70 of 25 August 1970 on the procedure for granting the premium for leaf tobacco (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 884/85 (4), provides for a system of supervision accompanied by checks on first processing and market preparation operations; whereas first processing and market preparation undertakings now subject certain varieties of tobacco to threshing, which consists in separating the whole tobacco leaf into the leafweb and the stem and veins; whereas in accordance with commercial practice the strips of leafweb are not less than 0,5 centimetre in diameter; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: lehttubaka jaoks lisatasu andmise korda k&auml;sitleva komisjoni 25. augusti 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1726/70, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 884/85, (4) n&auml;hakse ette j&auml;relevalves&uuml;steem, millega kaasneb esmat&ouml;&ouml;tlemise ja pakendamise kontroll; esmat&ouml;&ouml;tlemise ja pakendamise ettev&otilde;tetes eemaldatakse n&uuml;&uuml;d teatavat sorti tubakal leherootsud, kahestades terve tubakalehe lehekoeks ning varreks ja leheroodudeks; vastavalt kaubandustavadele on lehekoe riba laius v&auml;hemalt 0,5 sentimeetrit; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas first processing and market preparation operations for tobacco are attested by the premium certificate drawn up when the leaf tobacco is placed under supervision; whereas the details entered on the premium certificate are provided by the checks undertaken on entry to and exit from the place where the processing and market preparation operations are undertaken; whereas the premium certificate should specify, before the competent authority checks that the leaf tobacco and the baled tobacco tally, the quantity of tobacco obtained at the end of the first processing in the form of whole or cut leaves or strips; </inglise>
<eesti> tubaka esmat&ouml;&ouml;tlemist ja pakendamist t&otilde;endatakse lisatasu sertifikaadiga, mis koostatakse lehttubaka paigutamisel j&auml;relevalve alla; lisatasu sertifikaati kantavad andmed saadakse kontrollide p&otilde;hjal, mis teostatakse tubaka sisenemisel t&ouml;&ouml;tlemis- ja pakendamiskohta ning sealt v&auml;ljumisel; enne kui p&auml;dev asutus kontrollib lehttubaka ja pallpakendis tubaka vastavust, tuleks lisatasusertifikaadis t&auml;psustada esmat&ouml;&ouml;tluse tulemusel saadud tervete v&otilde;i l&otilde;igatud lehtede v&otilde;i ribade kogus; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the right to the premium accrues as soon as the tobacco leaves the place in which it was under supervision; whereas in the case of threshing, the marketing channels for strips and for the by-products consisting of stems and veins are different; whereas the latter have a very low market value and demand is extremely limited; whereas, therefore, in order not to penalize first processing and market preparation undertakings which undertake threshing, the right to the premium should accrue as soon as the strips leave the place of supervision; </inglise>
<eesti> &otilde;igus lisatasule saadakse kohe, kui tubakas on j&auml;relevalve alt &auml;ra viidud; leherootsude eemaldamise korral on turustuskanalid leheribade ning vartest ja roodudest koosnevate k&otilde;rvalsaaduste puhul erinevad; k&otilde;rvaltoodete turuv&auml;&auml;rtus on v&auml;ga madal ja n&otilde;udlus nende j&auml;rele on &auml;&auml;rmiselt piiratud; leherootsude eemaldamisega tegelevate esmat&ouml;&ouml;tlemise ja pakendamise ettev&otilde;tete kahjustamise v&auml;ltimiseks tuleks seep&auml;rast &otilde;igus lisatasule saada kohe, kui ribad on j&auml;relevalve alt &auml;ra viidud; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the amount of the premium is payable on the net weight of leaf tobacco after the competent authorities have checked that the quantities of tobacco brought under supervision and the quantities released therefrom tally; whereas it should be laid down that, in the case of threshing, the check on the tally must relate to the quantities of leaf tobacco placed under supervision and the quantities of strips released therefrom; whereas as regards release from supervision it should be laid down, in order to avoid any confusion with other products resulting from threshing, that only strips which are at least 0,5 centimetre in diameter are to be counted when checking the tally and establishing the right to the premium on their release from the place of supervision; </inglise>
<eesti> lisatasu summa makstakse lehttubaka netomassi alusel p&auml;rast seda, kui p&auml;devad asutused on kontrollinud, et j&auml;relevalve alla toodud tubakakogused vastavad j&auml;relevalve alt vabastatud kogustele; tuleks s&auml;testada, et leherootsude eemaldamise korral kontrollitakse j&auml;relevalve alla pandud lehttubaka koguste vastavust j&auml;relevalve alt vabastatud leheribade kogustele; seoses j&auml;relevalve alt vabastamisega tuleks selle v&auml;ltimiseks, et leheribasid ei aetaks segamini leherootsude eemaldamisel saadud muude toodetega, s&auml;testada, et vastavuse kontrollimisel ja p&auml;rast j&auml;relevalve alt &auml;raviimist lisatasu saamise &otilde;iguse andmisel tuleb arvestada &uuml;ksnes ribasid, mille laius on v&auml;hemalt 0,5 sentimeetrit; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Tobacco, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las tubakaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Regulation (EEC) No 1726/70 is hereby amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1726/70 muudetakse j&auml;rgmiselt. </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The following point (m') is inserted after point (m) of Article 2 (2): </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 2 punkti m j&auml;rele lisatakse punkt m': </eesti>
<inglise> '(m') The quantity of tobacco and/or strips with a diameter of at least 0,5 cm recorded on release from supervision; </inglise>
<eesti> "m') j&auml;relevalve alt vabastamisel registreeritud tubaka ja/v&otilde;i v&auml;hemalt 0,5 cm laiuste ribade kogus;". </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The first sentence of Article 6 (1) is replaced by the following: </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 6 l&otilde;ike 1 esimene lause asendatakse j&auml;rgmisega: </eesti>
<inglise> 'The right to the premium shall accrue as soon as the tobacco, in the form of whole or cut leaves and/or strips with a diameter of at least 0,5 cm, leaves the place in which it was under supervision. </inglise>
<eesti> "&Otilde;igus lisatasule saadakse kohe, kui tubakas on tervete v&otilde;i l&otilde;igatud lehtedena ja/v&otilde;i v&auml;hemalt 0,5 cm laiuste ribadena j&auml;relevalve alt &auml;ra viidud." </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> The first sentence of Article 6 (3) is replaced by the following: </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 6 l&otilde;ike 3 esimene lause asendatakse j&auml;rgmisega: </eesti>
<inglise> 'The competent authorities shall check, in respect of each undertaking, that the quantities of tobacco brought under supervision tally with those released therefrom in the form of whole or cut leaves and/or strips with a diameter of at least 0,5 cm. </inglise>
<eesti> "P&auml;devad asutused kontrollivad iga ettev&otilde;tte puhul, et j&auml;relevalve alla toodud tubakakogused vastavad j&auml;relevalve alt tervete v&otilde;i l&otilde;igatud lehtedena ja/v&otilde;i v&auml;hemalt 0,5 cm laiuste ribadena vabastatud tubakakogustele." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> It shall apply to tobacco from the 1985 and subsequent harvests. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;rust kohaldatakse 1985. aastal ja hiljem koristatud tubaka suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 2 April 1985. </inglise>
